{
  "stem": "20609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And believe it or not, I went to a couple of different farms because, one, I couldn't stand because it was so hard, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They never gave me anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I was treated like-- first of all, we never slept in the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were sleeping above the stable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And real-- no heat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "No nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The heat from the animals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the smell, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And the flies-- don't forget the flies in the summertime-- kept us warm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And not that I'm complaining about it, but I felt we should have been treated a little bit with more dignity.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, finally, at many times we used to say, well, let's get some money, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's get-- why can't we get a little pocket money?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So some places at the end, like in '42, we were getting a little pay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were actually considered cheap labor, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm very-- don't get me wrong, I'm very grateful for Denmark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[DRINKS] How many people were with you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How many kids were with you on those farms?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had about, I think in my group, were about 30 or 40 kids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stayed in that area.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nah, when we're talking about in my area, we're talking about one lived six kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- we were all on farms, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- The last job I had was-- was on a farm which was almost 15 kilometers to the Nyborg, to the city where we used to have school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at that time, I couldn't use my bicycle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The tires were shot, and we couldn't get any replacement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was sort of locked in on that-- that farm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- Were you with other kids on that farm?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
